body:
Hi, so I was connecting to an urf game when my internet unfortunately crashed while I was in the loading screen. Then the client said attemping to reconnect, so i closed since my internet wasnt working. After 30 seconds it cambe back up, i restarted the client, logged in and it automatically reconnected to the game. The loading screen page was black and it said that i couldnt connect to the match, but my internet was ok. So i restarted the client but that happened again. All of this happened 10 minutes ago. Now when i try to restart the client the same thing happens over and over but after 10 seconds I can only see the client that says "game is still in progress". Sorry for my bad english i hope you can understand. I have ruined a match for 9 other people because of this bug and my poor internet connection.

